            <span class="toggle_text "> Read More </span><svg id='arrow-svg' class="inline mx-1 mb-[2px]" fill="#ffffff" height="15px" width="15px" version="1.1" id="Layer_1" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" viewBox="-66 -66 462.00 462.00" xml:space="preserve" stroke="#ffffff" stroke-width="33"><g id="SVGRepo_bgCarrier" stroke-width="0"></g><g id="SVGRepo_tracerCarrier" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></g><g id="SVGRepo_iconCarrier"> <path id="XMLID_225_" d="M325.607,79.393c-5.857-5.857-15.355-5.858-21.213,0.001l-139.39,139.393L25.607,79.393 c-5.857-5.857-15.355-5.858-21.213,0.001c-5.858,5.858-5.858,15.355,0,21.213l150.004,150c2.813,2.813,6.628,4.393,10.606,4.393 s7.794-1.581,10.606-4.394l149.996-150C331.465,94.749,331.465,85.251,325.607,79.393z"></path> </g></svg>
            
          </button>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class=" notes-sub md:flex rounded-lg bg-white">
          <div class="text-black leading-7  md:w-1/3 m-5 md:border-r-[2px] p-4  border-r-zinc-200">
            <span class="font-bold"><svg
              class="float-left mt-2 mr-3"
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              width="10.605"
              height="15.555"
            >
              <path
                d="m2.828 15.555 7.777-7.779L2.828 0 0 2.828l4.949 4.948L0 12.727l2.828 2.828"
                fill="#172177"></path>
            </svg></span> Submitting the following details is mandatory for fund release in the fund request form under the report section: <br><br><ul class="list-decimal"> <li> <form> <span class="underline text-[#172177]"><a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1G6t4MwF0ql5Sbgh3nVEi44QCcR53kwijxG81-288hWE/edit" target="_blank" >Startups from Institution in the</a></span> form till date (Without CIN/DIPP No/ Unique ID will make the idea to be considered as Ideation stage/pre incubation stage. If unfilled no will be considered as zero)</li><li><span class="underline text-[#172177]"><a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1G6t4MwF0ql5Sbgh3nVEi44QCcR53kwijxG81-288hWE/edit" target="_blank">Patents Generated from the Institution</a></span> (if unfilled no will be considered as zero)</li><li>Previous activity reports</li><li><span class="underline text-[#172177]"><a href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1oYr7nN5xWuy6zRkLjdebT5zFrX_eU-Yjh9n82hJMu1I/edit#gid=0" target="_blank">Action Plan for the coming year</a></span> (Should be submitted when requested)</li>
          </div>
          <div class="text-black  leading-7  md:w-1/3 m-5 md:border-r-[2px] p-4 border-r-zinc-200">
            <span class="font-bold"><svg
              class="float-left mt-2 mr-3"
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              width="10.605"
              height="15.555"
            >
              <path
                d="m2.828 15.555 7.777-7.779L2.828 0 0 2.828l4.949 4.948L0 12.727l2.828 2.828"
                fill="#172177"></path>
            </svg></span> Please keep the following information ready while submitting the fund request: <br><br><ul class="list-decimal"><li><span class="underline text-[#172177]"><a href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1yk6PQdBpQQAZPIWZ6Tnfn_GMGZmu453Ql_GztiUULuE/edit#gid=0" target="_blank">Details of PoCs</a></span> (If more faculties are involved in IEDC activities)</li><li>Details of Nodal Officers</li><li>Details of Head of the institute</li><li><span class="underline text-[#172177]"></span><a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1fuG7JcEEc6hxEx6RLoifhsCxUHFPjy_YKUvV3x6B9BY/edit" target="_blank">IEDC Execom</a> 2023-2024 details are submitted <span class="underline text-[#172177]"><a href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1oAeNYYSpQkeun20pVx3K2qKLkHFyivj-bSnfymQHINQ/edit#gid=0" target="_blank">and the excel sheet is ready</span></a></li><li>Bank Account Details are submitted</li>           </div>
           <div class="text-black  leading-7 p-4 md:w-1/3 m-5">
            <span class="font-bold"><svg
              class="float-left mt-2 mr-3"
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              width="10.605"
              height="15.555"
            >
              <path
                d="m2.828 15.555 7.777-7.779L2.828 0 0 2.828l4.949 4.948L0 12.727l2.828 2.828"
                fill="#172177"></path>
            </svg></span> Please Keep the following documents ready in specified Format: <br> <br><ul class="list-decimal"><li>IEDC Activities Report 2022 - 2023</li><li>IEDC Activities Report - Previous Years</li><li>Auditors Report, Fund Utilisation Certificate & Signed Statement of Expenditures with UDIN no <span class="underline text-[#172177]"><a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/16s-oV1cZlzPpp4eFs3f9EEmPuQBqRBJqw4-t82bzolM/edit" target="_blank">(as per the prescribed format is mandatory</span>).</a></li><li>Scanned Passbook Front Page</li><li>Account statement till 31 March 2023</li><li><span class="underline text-[#172177]"><a href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1oYr7nN5xWuy6zRkLjdebT5zFrX_eU-Yjh9n82hJMu1I/edit" target="_blank">IEDC Action Plan 2023 - 2024 (as per the prescribed format with details of expenditure)</span></a>. (Should be submitted when requested)</li><li>Declaration in College letterhead <span class="underline text-[#172177]"><a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/148-UoLYGP9TeTAuUGnPy_s8Rin2fD_QcpiGOY0WkXIc/edit" target="_blank">(as per the prescribed format is mandatory)</span></a>.</li>           </div>
        </div>
        <div
        class="fund-links mx:auto md:grid md:gap-6 lg:grid-cols-4 lg:grid-rows-3 md:grid-rows-4 md:grid-cols-3 place-content-center p-7"
      >
        <Card
          title="Fund Request Submitted IEDCs"
